<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.5.2">
<l>cīyi ṉālceṟin tēṟiya puṇmēl</l>
<l rend="indent">ceṟṟa lēṟiku ḻampirun teṅkum</l>
<l>īyi ṉālarip puṇṭuma yaṅki</l>
<l rend="indent">yellai vāycceṉṟu cērvataṉ muṉṉam</l>
<l>vāyi ṉālnamō nāraṇā veṉṟu</l>
<l rend="indent">matta kattiṭaik kaikaḷaik kūppi</l>
<l>pōyi ṉālpiṉṉai yitticaik keṉṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">piṇaik koṭukkilum pōkavoṭ ṭārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before going and reaching the edge [of death],</l>
<l rend="indent">being maddened by itching because of flies,</l>
<l rend="indent">maggots spreading and mingling on raised sores</l>
<l rend="indent">thick with pus everywhere,</l>
<l>if [you] go, joining [your] hands in worship atop [your] head,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] saying with [your] mouth, “Namo Nāraṇa”,</l>
<l>afterward, even if given a guarantee</l>
<l rend="indent">of perpetually [returning] to this place,</l>
<l rend="indent">He will not allow [you] to go.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
